01:23.430 --> 01:26.598
Well, uh, it seems
to have settled for now.

01:26.632 --> 01:29.234
Might want
to keep your distance.

01:29.268 --> 01:31.202
I might.

01:34.975 --> 01:38.679
Time for our patient's
morning fix.

01:38.713 --> 01:41.815
Meet me in the command post
in five.

